item.title: Unreconized server errors - How do I fix?
item.dc:creator: @TankedJare TankedJare
item.description:
@TankedJare wrote:

I wouldn’t know where to start for searching for coding problems.
(Just downloaded it and was testing it)

Is v.6 the newest version of java?
I have that.

Also, when I pressed “edit” on the runserver.exe it showed me

[code]@echo off
title GangScape - Server
java -Xmx1024m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.17-ga-bin.jar server
tskill java

Pause[/code]

Could that be my problem?
And by the way I added pause, because it was opening then closing.
